    <div id="popup-gurdon" class="popup-overlay" onclick="closePopup('popup-gurdon')">
      <div class="popup-box" onclick="event.stopPropagation();">
        <p>Prize motivation: “for the discovery that mature cells can be reprogrammed to become pluripotent”</p>
        <p>In 1962, John Gurdon removed the nucleus of a fertilized egg cell from a frog and replaced it with the nucleus of a cell taken from a tadpole's intestine. This modified egg cell grew into a new frog, proving that the mature cell still contained the genetic information needed to form all types of cells.</p>
        <button onclick="closePopup('popup-gurdon')">Close</button>
